{"id":"rd-001","subject":"Fetch current user analytics","description":"Provide a detailed report on current user metrics, including active users, sign-ups, and any notable trends. Ensure this is formatted for recurring updates.","status":"done","priority":"normal","assignee":"riftdecks-worker-1","depends_on":[],"blocks":[],"labels":[],"metadata":null,"created_at":"2026-02-21T17:07:50.276870546Z","updated_at":"2026-02-21T17:11:18.791105760Z","closed_at":"2026-02-21T17:11:18.791102795Z","closed_reason":"---\n\n## RiftDecks Analytics Report — Feb 21, 2026\n\n### Realtime\n**2 active visitors** on site right now.\n\n---\n\n### Traffic Overview\n\n| Period | Visitors | Pageviews | Bounce Rate | Avg Session |\n|--------|----------|-----------|-------------|-------------|\n| Today (partial) | 68 | 316 | 48% | 5m 24s |\n| 7 days | 418 | 5,179 | 53% | 7m 54s |\n| 30 days | 429 | 5,326 | 52% | 8m 26s |\n\n**Notable trend**: 30-day and 7-day numbers are nearly identical — almost all traffic arrived Feb 15–21. Sharp growth spike starting Feb 17, peaking yesterday (Feb 20: 143 visitors, 1,543 pageviews).\n\n| Date | Visitors | Pageviews |\n|------|----------|-----------|\n| Feb 15 | 20 | 305 |\n| Feb 16 | 15 | 176 |\n| Feb 17 | 28 | 1,051 |\n| Feb 18 | 46 | 1,090 |\n| Feb 19 | 98 | 698 |\n| Feb 20 | **143** | **1,543** |\n| Feb 21 (partial) | 68 | 316 |\n\n---\n\n### Conversion Funnel (7 days)\n\n| Stage | Visitors | Rate vs Previous |\n|-------|----------|-----------------|\n| Visitors | 418 | — |\n| `deck_click` | 98 | 23% |\n| `deck_view` | 103 | ~100% |\n| `checkout_click` | 3 | **3%** ← big drop |\n| `purchase_complete` | 2 | 67% |\n\n**Critical bottleneck**: deck view → checkout is only ~3%. 103 visitors viewed a deck, only 3 hit \"Lock In.\"\n\n**Purchases this week: 3 transactions, 2 unique buyers.**\n\nTop checkout intent by deck: Azir (2), Draven (1), Viktor (1).\n\n---\n\n### Deck Interest (7d Clicks)\n\n| Rank | Deck | Clicks |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 1 | Draven | 55 |\n| 2 | Fiora | 49 |\n| 3 | Irelia | 40 |\n| 4 | Kaisa | 42 |\n| 5 | Ezreal | 27 |\n| 6 | Viktor | 24 |\n| 7 | Sivir | 19 |\n| 8 | Ornn | 16 |\n| 9 | Azir | 15 |\n| 10 | Lucian | 13 |\n\n---\n\n### Traffic Sources\n\n| Source | Visitors | Share |\n|--------|----------|-------|\n| Google (organic) | 230 | 55% |\n| Direct | 167 | 40% |\n| Stripe returns | 4 | — |\n| Facebook | 3 | — |\n\nSEO is working. Paid traffic is negligible.\n\n---\n\n### Geo\n\nUS (125, 30%) leads, followed by Spain, Germany, Italy (~28% combined). Notable: 12 HK visitors — likely aware of the Chinese card sourcing.\n\n---\n\n### Device Split\n\n- **Mobile**: 58% — majority of traffic is on phone\n- **Desktop**: 37%\n\n---\n\n### Flags\n\n- `/steal` — 19 visitors to an unknown page (not in standard routes). Worth investigating.\n- Deck view → checkout conversion is very low (3%). Price, trust, or UX friction.\n- Traffic is very new (started ~Feb 15). No baseline yet for week-over-week comparison."}
{"id":"rd-002","subject":"Fetch today's user analytics","description":"Provide a detailed report on today's user metrics, including active users, sign-ups, and any notable trends. Ensure the data is accurate and not a random number.","status":"done","priority":"normal","assignee":"riftdecks-worker-2","depends_on":[],"blocks":[],"labels":[],"metadata":null,"created_at":"2026-02-21T17:08:03.009790988Z","updated_at":"2026-02-21T17:11:34.579684846Z","closed_at":"2026-02-21T17:11:34.579681870Z","closed_reason":"Here's today's analytics report for RiftDecks (Feb 21, 2026):\n\n---\n\n## RiftDecks — Today's Analytics\n\n### Overview\n| Metric | Today | Yesterday |\n|--------|-------|-----------|\n| Unique Visitors | **68** | 143 |\n| Pageviews | **316** | 1,543 |\n| Bounce Rate | 48% | — |\n| Avg Session | 5.4 min | — |\n| Realtime | **2 active** | — |\n\n*Note: today is still in progress — yesterday was the biggest day of the week.*\n\n### 7-Day Traffic Trend\nTraffic has been ramping sharply: 15 → 20 → 28 → 46 → 98 → **143** → 68 (today, partial).\n\n### Conversion Funnel\n| Stage | Visitors |\n|-------|---------|\n| Landing page | 62 |\n| Deck click | 21 |\n| Deck view | 24 |\n| Add to cart | 2 |\n| Checkout initiated | 1 |\n| **Purchase complete** | **0** |\n\nNo purchases today yet. One visitor reached checkout (`unified_cart_checkout`).\n\n### Top Decks by Interest\n1. **Draven** — 9 views, 6 clicks\n2. **Kaisa** — 9 views, 4 clicks\n3. **Fiora** — 6 views, 5 clicks\n4. **Irelia** — 4 views, 3 clicks\n\n### Traffic Sources\n- **76% Google** (52 visitors) — strong organic search\n- **25% Direct**\n\n### Audience\n- **57% mobile** / 40% desktop\n- Top markets: US (26), Canada (6), Germany (5), Spain (5), Italy (5)\n\n---\n\n**Key takeaway**: Traffic is strong coming off yesterday's peak. The landing-to-deck-view conversion looks healthy (~35%), but the cart→checkout drop-off is steep — only 1 visitor hit checkout from 2 add-to-carts today. Worth watching as the day progresses."}
