{"id":"rd-004","subject":"Analyze and Improve All RiftDecks Analytics Infrastructure","description":"1. Audit current analytics setup (Plausible, button clicks, user flows). 2. Enhance all tracking to capture maximum actionable data (e.g., funnel drops, retention triggers). 3. Configure Plausible dashboard for comprehensive visibility (custom metrics, segmentation). 4. Ensure 'absurd' granularity—no metric left behind. 5. Report back with upgrade summary and net-new capabilities.","status":"done","priority":"normal","assignee":"riftdecks-worker-1","depends_on":[],"blocks":[],"labels":[],"metadata":null,"created_at":"2026-02-21T17:17:56.910853653Z","updated_at":"2026-02-21T17:21:37.833983922Z","closed_at":"2026-02-21T17:21:37.833980876Z","closed_reason":""}
